  select_if(is_numeric) %>%

More info on distribution with boxplots

diamonds %>%
  select_if(is.numeric) %>%
  gather(key = "ind", value = "values") %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = ind, y = values)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  coord_flip() +
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_fill_grey()
